                            <comment id="13447721" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Tue, 4 Sep 2012 14:30:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I committed a first iteration - I have more refinement/improvement coming. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13448123" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Tue, 4 Sep 2012 22:29:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I only solved the issue when stopping the leader - there was also a similar issue on session expiration (the leaders update queue could to be emptying as we elect a new leader and beyond). I fixed this as well by shutting down the executor on session expiration and creating a new one for further use.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
